hebookseller.com/news/belinda-ioni-rasmussen-appointed-president-and-publisher-at-walker-books-group" >Belinda Ioni Rasmussen appointed president and publisher at Walker Books Group</a></h2></div></div></div><div class="aos-de-al2563 aos-SHC aos-FL aos-MTM aos-DFM aos-W50 aos-Br3-W100-KP aos-ArticleType-Highlight"><div class="aos-SHCi aos-FL100 aos-PosR aos-OFH aos-H100 aos-DFi aos-DFW"><div class="aos-ArticleTextContainer aos-OFH aos-DynWidth aos-FL100"><h2 class="aos-ArticleTitle aos-DS21-H2 aos-FL100 aos-BW aos-M0 aos-DF aos-TAL"><a href="https://www.thebookseller.com/rights/white-rabbit-signs-leeroy-thornhills-getting-high-in-the-prodigy" >White Rabbit signs Leeroy Thornhillâs Getting High in the Prodigy</a></h2></div></div></div><div class="aos-de-al2563 aos-SHC aos-FL aos-MTM aos-DFM aos-W50 aos-Br3-W100-KP aos-Br3-DN aos-ArticleType-Highlight"><div class="aos-SHCi aos-FL100 aos-PosR aos-OFH aos-H100 aos-DFi aos-DFW"><div class="aos-ArticleTextContainer aos-OFH aos-DynWidth aos-FL100"><h2 class="aos-ArticleTitle aos-DS21-H2 aos-FL100 aos-BW aos-M0 aos-DF aos-TAL"><a href="https://www.thebookseller.com/news/dissolution-author-c-j-sansom-dies-aged-71" >Dissolution author C J Sansom dies, aged 71</a></h2></div></div></div><div class="aos-de-al2563 aos-SHC aos-FL aos-MTM aos-DFM aos-W50 aos-Br3-W100-KP aos-Br3-DN aos-ArticleType-Highlight"><div class="aos-SHCi aos-FL100 aos-PosR aos-OFH aos-H100 aos-DFi aos-DFW"><div class="aos-ArticleTextContainer aos-OFH aos-DynWidth aos-FL100"><h2 class="aos-ArticleTitle aos-DS21-H2 aos-FL100 aos-BW aos-M0 aos-DF aos-TAL"><a href="https://www.thebookseller.com/news/fenella-bates-appointed-as-puffin-non-fiction-publisher" >Fenella Bates appointed as Puffin non-fiction publisher</a></h2></div></div></div><div class="aos-de-al2563 aos-SHC aos-FL aos-MTM aos-DFM aos-W50 aos-Br3-W100-KP aos-Br3-DN aos-ArticleType-Highlight"><div class="aos-SHCi aos-FL100 aos-PosR aos-OFH aos-H100 aos-DFi aos-DFW"><div class="aos-ArticleTextContain